bug.short_desc: qx.ui.table dispose bug on IE6 after disabling column

long_desc.thetext:
If eg. on demo/test/Table_1.htm a column is made invisible by unchecking th column in the table context menu and the page is reloaded (dispose is done) there following error is displayed:
"Modification of property "parent" failed with exception: TypeError - 'this.getParent()' is Null or not an object".
A screen snapshot is attached which shows the bug.
The bug only shows up in InternetExplorer 6 but not in FireFox 1.5
No, nothing new. I'm currently working on another project. Any contributions are welcome.
